<p>I post my code that removes an array element in place, and reduce the array length as well.</p>

<pre><code>function removeElement(idx, arr) {
    // Check the index value
    if (idx &lt; 0 || idx &gt;= arr.length) {
        return;
    }
    // Shift the elements
    for (var i = idx; i &gt; 0; --i) {
        arr[i] = arr[i - 1];
    }
    // Remove the first element in array
    arr.shift();
}
</code></pre>
